{"thag14.1:0.1":"Theragatha 14.1 ","thag14.1:0.2":"Cuddasakanipata ","thag14.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag14.1:0.4":"Khadiravaniyarevatattheragatha ","thag14.1:1.1":"“Yada aham pabbajito, ","thag14.1:1.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag14.1:1.3":"Nabhijanami sankappam, ","thag14.1:1.4":"anariyam dosasamhitam. ","thag14.1:2.1":"‘Ime hannantu vajjhantu, ","thag14.1:2.2":"dukkham pappontu panino’; ","thag14.1:2.3":"Sankappam nabhijanami, ","thag14.1:2.4":"imasmim dighamantare. ","thag14.1:3.1":"Mettanca abhijanami, ","thag14.1:3.2":"appamanam subhavitam; ","thag14.1:3.3":"Anupubbam paricitam, ","thag14.1:3.4":"yatha buddhena desitam. ","thag14.1:4.1":"Sabbamitto sabbasakho, ","thag14.1:4.2":"sabbabhutanukampako; ","thag14.1:4.3":"Mettacittanca bhavemi, ","thag14.1:4.4":"abyapajjarato sada. ","thag14.1:5.1":"Asamhiram asankuppam, ","thag14.1:5.2":"cittam amodayamaham; ","thag14.1:5.3":"Brahmaviharam bhavemi, ","thag14.1:5.4":"akapurisasevitam. ","thag14.1:6.1":"Avitakkam samapanno, ","thag14.1:6.2":"sammasambuddhasavako; ","thag14.1:6.3":"Ariyena tunhibhavena, ","thag14.1:6.4":"upeto hoti tavade. ","thag14.1:7.1":"Yathapi pabbato selo, ","thag14.1:7.2":"acalo suppatitthito; ","thag14.1:7.3":"Evam mohakkhaya bhikkhu, ","thag14.1:7.4":"pabbatova na vedhati. ","thag14.1:8.1":"Ananganassa posassa, ","thag14.1:8.2":"niccam sucigavesino; ","thag14.1:8.3":"Valaggamattam papassa, ","thag14.1:8.4":"abbhamattamva khayati. ","thag14.1:9.1":"Nagaram yatha paccantam, ","thag14.1:9.2":"guttam santarabahiram; ","thag14.1:9.3":"Evam gopetha attanam, ","thag14.1:9.4":"khano vo ma upaccaga. ","thag14.1:10.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag14.1:10.2":"nabhinandami jivitam; ","thag14.1:10.3":"Kalanca patikankhami, ","thag14.1:10.4":"nibbisam bhatako yatha. ","thag14.1:11.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag14.1:11.2":"… pe ","thag14.1:11.3":"… ","thag14.1:11.4":"sampajano patissato. ","thag14.1:12.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag14.1:12.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag14.1:12.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag14.1:12.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag14.1:13.1":"Yassa catthaya pabbajito, ","thag14.1:13.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag14.1:13.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag14.1:13.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thag14.1:14.1":"Sampadethappamadena, ","thag14.1:14.2":"esa me anusasani; ","thag14.1:14.3":"Handaham parinibbissam, ","thag14.1:14.4":"vippamuttomhi sabbadhi”ti. ","thag14.1:14.5":"… Khadiravaniyarevato thero …. "}